data.description: Introducing a charming ranch-style home that effortlessly combines comfort and convenience. Nestled on a spacious lot, this property boasts a generous backyard complete with a practical shed, perfect for your storage needs. The master bedroom features a recently rehabbed bathroom, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. With central air just two years old, you'll stay cool and comfortable year-round. The well-designed kitchen offers ample space for both cooking and dining, while a wooden fence surrounds the property for added privacy. Inside, you'll find a high-efficiency furnace and an Eco B thermostat, ensuring energy efficiency and eco-friendliness. This is not just a house; it's your dream home!
